						"then": [
							{
								"type": "text",
								"text": "The Gamer Clown goes very still for a moment.\n\n\"...I'm impressed,\" they say. \"Genuinely.\"\n\nThey tilt their head.\n\n\"You wouldn't like me when I'm surprised.\"",
								"clear": true,
								"no_continue": true
							},
							{
								"type": "text",
								"text": "They split into three.\n\nThe new one's mask is frozen mid-gasp — wide eyes, open mouth, arrested mid-shock.\n\n\"Get your dice out,\" they say. The other two agree, very quietly, like this happens often.",
								"clear": false,
								"no_continue": false
							},
